FBIS4-19889 "drweu079_p_94009" FBIS-WEU-94-079 Daily Report 24 Apr 1994 GREECE Strong Explosion Damages UN High Commission Building Strong Explosion Damages UN High Commission Building NC2404051394 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 0400 GMT 24 Apr 94 NC2404051394 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] A strong explosion occurred at 0512 [0212 GMT] today at the UN High Commission offices at 59 Skoufa Street in Kolonaki. The explosion, which happened inside the UN offices, caused extensive damage inside the building and to nearby apartment buildings. Five minutes after the explosion, an unidentified man called FLASH Radio [private station] saying that no one should go near the UN High Commission building because a stronger explosion would follow.
